dnl SYNOPSIS
dnl
dnl   AM_PYTHON2_MODULE(modname[, fatal])
dnl
dnl DESCRIPTION
dnl
dnl   Checks for Python 2 module.
dnl
dnl   If fatal is non-empty then absence of a module will trigger an error.
dnl
